    "recognition_paragraph": {
      "interpretive_text": "What you want is depth, a few people who actually know you, alongside something of your own to make. What you can't stand is people who never talk about the important things, or only ever consuming and creating nothing.",
      "token_text": "Relationship Rebuilder and Creator."
    },
    "pattern_paragraph": {
      "interpretive_text": "All seven readings sit at high. Attention moving without much registering; mostly absent in the relationships he has.",
